FBIS3-49935 "dreeu009__a94032" FBIS-EEU-94-009-A Document Type:Daily Report 13 January 1994 ANNEX Slovakia HZDS Popularity Declines to 14 Percent AU1201080894 Prague CTK in English 1655 GMT 11 Jan 94 AU1201080894 Prague CTK Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Bratislava, Jan 11 (CTK) -- The governing Movement for a Democratic Slovakia (HZDS) is most popular in central Slovakia, while the opposition Democratic Left Party's (SDL) stronghold is in east Slovakia and Bratislava, a poll conducted by the Slovak Statistical Office in December 1993 revealed. ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Voting Preferences Between September and December | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- | |Sept |Oct |Nov |Dec | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |No preference |45 |40 |- |44 | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Movement for |15 |17 |16 |14 | |a Democratic | | | | | |Slovakia | | | | | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Democratic Le-|12 |12 |16 |12 | |ft Party | | | | | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Slovak Nation-|7 |7 |7 |5 | |al Party | | | | | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Christian Dem-|7 |9 |9 |8 | |ocratic Movem-| | | | | |ent | | | | | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Hungarian Chr-|4 |5 |5 |5 | |istian Democr-| | | | | |atic Movement | | | | | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Green Party |3 |3 |4 |3 | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Slovak Social |2 |2 |-- |-- | |Democratic Pa-| | | | | |rty | | | | | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Alliance of S-|-- |2 |2 |2 | |lovak Democra-| | | | | |t